                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The list of persons present at this dinner is taken from the Log, <hi
                        rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_845">p. 845</ref>, except for
                    Leahy, whose presence is noted in his Diary (Leahy Papers). No record of the
                    discussion has been found.</p>
